title: Arbor Snowboards :: Product Profiles - A-Frame
description:
A contemporary big-mountain gun for riders who want superior on-edge camber performance and exceptional float in powder. The A-frame will lock and hold a deeply carved line, provide powerful control in the steeps, and deliver amazing stability at speed.
To learn more about the A-Frame visit: arborcollective.com/snowboards/products/a-frame/
